OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day to come
OL,6,Fwith some light drizzly rain on and
OL,7,Foff and perhaps heavy and prolonged in
OL,8,Fplaces. The far northwest may stay
OL,9,Fdrier albeit cloudy. Winds often light
OL,10,Fbut breezy at times. Less mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain clearing eastwards this
OL,13,Fevening leaving a drier night with
OL,14,Fclear spells developing. Showers may
OL,15,Faffect northern and western coastal
OL,16,Fregions. Turning chilly in the
OL,17,Fcountryside with isolated fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
