OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry for many with sunny
OL,6,Fperiods and feeling reasonable with
OL,7,Flight winds. Isolated showers are
OL,8,Fpossible, mainly in coastal districts,
OL,9,Fwith showers pushing eastwards during
OL,10,Fthe evening. Freshening winds later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWetter
OL,13,Fand windier on Sunday with occasional
OL,14,Fdrizzly rain, this most frequent over
OL,15,Fthe hills. Generally drier on Monday
OL,16,Fbut showery rain still possible.
OL,17,FPerhaps brighter on Tuesday. Staying
OL,18,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
